# couchbase-capella_cloud_project_snapshot_backups (Data Source)

The snapshot backups data source retrieves snapshot backups associated with a project

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "couchbase-capella_cloud_project_snapshot_backups" "existing_cloud_project_snapshot_backups" {
  organization_id = "aaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeee"
  project_id      = "aaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeee"
}
```

- `project_id` (String) The GUID4 ID of the project.

- `per_page` (Number) Sets the number of results you would like to have on each page.
- `sort_by` (String)
